Description:
Summon a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_VoidGauntlet.VoidGauntlet_NullChamber_AoE.Radius]}m&lt;/font&gt; radius circular rift of Void energy at your feet for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;6s&lt;/font&gt; that deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_NullChamber_DoT.HealthModifierDamageBased * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_void_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage per second to enemies and grants &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;empower&lt;/font&gt; to self and friendlies, increasing damage by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_NullChamber_Empower.DMGCorruption * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

(This effect cannot be dispelled.)&lt;/font&gt;

Costs &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[ManaCosts_Player.VoidGauntlet_NullChamber.ManaCost]}&lt;/font&gt; Mana.

Unleash a Void-infused scream, dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.VoidGauntlet_Scream.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_void_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage, &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;staggering&lt;/font&gt; and inflicting &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;root&lt;/font&gt; to enemies &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;5m&lt;/font&gt; in front of you. Disables enemy movement for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_Scream.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;.

Costs &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[ManaCosts_Player.VoidGauntlet_Scream.ManaCost]}&lt;/font&gt; Mana.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

Taunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your void gauntlet, hits with this ability inflict taunt for {[DamageTable.VoidGauntlet_Scream.TauntDuration]}s. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)&lt;/font&gt;

On successful ability hit, gain a stack of &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Void Essence&lt;/font&gt;. At &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;6&lt;/font&gt; stacks, consume all stacks and gain a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_VoidGauntlet.VoidGauntlet_SiphonAura_AoE.Radius]}m&lt;/font&gt; aura that &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;heals&lt;/font&gt; self and friendlies for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_SiphonAura_Heal.HealthModifierDamageBased * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; weapon damage and deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_SiphonAura_DoT.HealthModifierDamageBased * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_void_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage per second to enemies within. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_VoidGauntlet.VoidGauntlet_SiphonAura_AoE.Duration * .001]}s&lt;/font&gt; duration. 
&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Healing scales exclusively with Focus.) 
({[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_SiphonAura_Timer.BaseDuration]}s cooldown.)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

(This effect cannot be dispelled.)&lt;/font&gt;

Fire an &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;unblockable&lt;/font&gt; orb that passes through enemies, deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.VoidGauntlet_DecayingOrb.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_void_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage and inflicts &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Disintegrate&lt;/font&gt;, dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_Disintegrate.HealthModifierDamageBased * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_void_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage per second and reducing target's armor by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_Disintegrate.PhysicalArmor * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_Disintegrate.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Stacks up to {[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_Disintegrate.StackMax]} times.)&lt;/font&gt;

At max range, it transforms into a healing orb and returns, &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;healing&lt;/font&gt; friendlies for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_DecayingOrb_Heal.HealthModifierDamageBased * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; weapon damage per second for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_DecayingOrb_Heal.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Healing scales exclusively with Focus.)&lt;/font&gt;

Costs &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[ManaCosts_Player.VoidGauntlet_DecayingOrb.ManaCost]}&lt;/font&gt; Mana.

Fire a projectile dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.VoidGauntlet_DrainingTether.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_void_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage that tethers you to an enemy for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_DrainingTether_Weaken.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;, &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;weakening&lt;/font&gt; it and &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;empowering&lt;/font&gt; you by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.VoidGauntlet_DrainingTether_Weaken.DMGCorruption * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt;. The tether ends early if the target moves beyond &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_VoidGauntlet.VoidGauntlet_DrainingTether.Radius]}m&lt;/font&gt;.

Costs &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[ManaCosts_Player.VoidGauntlet_DrainingTether.ManaCost]}&lt;/font&gt; Mana.

&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Tether remains active after weapon swap.)&lt;/font&gt;
